Among the proposed regulations, there are tax facilities for managers and benefits for the mobile public: viewers will be able to enter the restricted area, and there will be special rates for parking and in certain parking areas.
"It's an initiative that please me" observes Giuseppe Tornatore "and I hope that other cities will follow the example of Bologna by putting in place other measures.
